				<div class="post box" id="post-12531">
				
					<h2 class="singleh2"><a title="Permanent Link to A Field Guide to Sports Egos" href="http://www.mensjournal.com/a-field-guide-to-sports-egos" rel="bookmark">A Field Guide to Sports Egos</a></h2>
                    <div class="date-comments">
                        <p class="fl">Tue, Mar 2, 2010</p>    
                        <p class="fr"><a href="http://www.mensjournal.com/category/cover_stories" title="View all posts in Cover Stories" rel="category tag">Cover Stories</a>, <a href="http://www.mensjournal.com/category/sports" title="View all posts in Sports" rel="category tag">Sports</a></p>		        
                    </div>        
                    
                    		
					<div class="entry">
                    
                                                
						
                        <div class="sb_row" id="sb_row_top">
                            
